    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="实分析"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#实分析"></a> 实分析</h1><p>因为感觉实分析很有趣也很重要，所以就决定要重新维护起博客。😏<br />学校里实分析课用的教材是 <strong>《实变函数论》（第三版）——周民强</strong> ，<br />所以博客的主干还是教材和课上的笔记。<br />当然，如果在别的地方看到一些有意思的东西，我也会加进去的。😄<br />（拜托坚持更新下去，<s>就算是为了每一篇文章里面放一个小姐姐！</s>）</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/xwilludelu/pic/raw/master/pic/%E5%AE%9E%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90.jpg" alt="实分析" /><br />😘</p><h2 id="亮闪闪的传送门"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#亮闪闪的传送门"></a> 亮闪闪的传送门</h2><p><a href="#page1">第一章 集合与点集</a><br /><a href="#page2">第二章 Lebesgue测度</a>(施工中)<br /><a href="#page3">第三章 可测函数</a>(施工中)<br /><a href="#page4">第四章 Lebesgue积分</a>(施工中)<br /><a href="#page5">第五章 微分与不定积分</a>(施工中)<br /><a href="#page4">第六章 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>L</mi><mi>P</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L^P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8413309999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">L</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8413309999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>空间</a>(施工中)</p><div id = "page1"></div><br><h2 id="第一章-集合与点集"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#第一章-集合与点集"></a> 第一章 集合与点集</h2><p>1.集合的运算：一元：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E^{C}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8413309999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8413309999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> , <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathcal{P}(E)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.08222em;">P</span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> .<br />二元：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>∩</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cap</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.55556em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">∩</span></span></span></span> , <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>∪</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cup</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.55556em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">∪</span></span></span></span> , <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">\</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\backslash</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">\</span></span></span></span> , <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">△</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\triangle</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord">△</span></span></span></span> , <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>×</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\times</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">×</span></span></span></span> .<br />a.其中在同一个空间内的几种操作可以由（任？）两种运算生成。如：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>∩</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><msup><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cap , E^{C}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.035771em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord">∩</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8413309999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />所以在一定的空间内我们可以通过只考虑两种运算下的性质而推知其他运算的性质。<br />（对De Morgan法则的理解）<br />b.我们还可以考虑这些运算在特征函数上的操作。<br /><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>E</mi><mi>C</mi></msup><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">E^{C}:1-\chi(E)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8413309999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8413309999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span><br /><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>∩</mo><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cap:1-\chi(A)\chi(B)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.55556em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">∩</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span><br /><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>∪</mo><mo>:</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cup:\chi(A)+\chi(B)-\chi(A)\chi(B)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.55556em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">∪</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span><br /><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">\</mi><mo>:</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\backslash:\chi(A)-\chi(B)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">\</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span><br /><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">△</mi><mo>:</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>χ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\triangle:|\chi(A)-\chi(B)|</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord">△</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">:</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">χ</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord">∣</span></span></span></span><br />c.幂集<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathcal{P}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.08222em;">P</span></span></span></span></span>:所有子集的集族，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>d</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="script">P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>2</mn><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>d</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">card(\mathcal{P}(E))=2^{card(E)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.08222em;">P</span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8879999999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">2</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8879999999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">a</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">d</span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />d.笛卡尔积<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo>×</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\times</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">×</span></span></span></span>:生成的所有二元组的集合，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>d</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>d</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>d</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>B</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">card(A\times B)=card(A)card(B)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord mathdefault">c</span><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span><br />2.集合间关系：包含关系下是偏序的——不能普遍比较，但是有自反，<strong>反对称</strong>，传递性。<br />a.佐恩引理：在任何一非空的偏序集中，若任何链都有上界，则此偏序集内必然存在（至少一枚）极大元。<br />佐恩引理等价于选择公理。<br />3.集合的极限：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mover accent="true"><mi>lim</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="true">‾</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding